\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u1ecdn n\u1ebfn duy nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean Instagram \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t n\u0103m k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb l\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ph\u00e1p. \"Ch\u00fac m\u1eebng sinh nh\u1eadt v\u1edbi t\u00f4i. K\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m m\u1ed9t n\u0103m \u1edf trong t\u1ee7\", Ben Arfa vi\u1ebft.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tien ve Ben Arfa troll doi bong chu quan PSG hinh anh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ben Arfa troll \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/7/cc-1413-1523008619.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ben Arfa t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c l\u1ec5 vui v\u1ebb. \u1ea2nh: NN.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAnh c\u00f3 32 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n trong m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho PSG sau khi gia nh\u1eadp t\u1eeb Nice v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do n\u0103m 2016.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean b\u01b0\u1edbc sang m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Newcastle kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Unai Emery tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng. L\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng anh ch\u01a1i cho PSG l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Avranches \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Coupe de France, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ben Arfa ghi hai b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 31 tu\u1ed5i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 anh r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Parc des Princes v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y sau khi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"Cu\u1ed9c phi\u00eau l\u01b0u v\u1edbi PSG k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00e0 b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi m\u1eb7c chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n lu\u00f4n y\u00eau CLB n\u00e0y\", Ben Arfa n\u00f3i nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi cu\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo ngoisao.net<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"869","checkdouble":"183721"},{"date":"14:35 07/04","title":"V\u1ee3 Lionel Messi khoe \u1ea3nh con trai g\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng tu\u1ed5i","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/7/vo-lionel-messi-khoe-anh-con-trai-gan-mot-thang-tuoi.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"868","checkdouble":"183722"},{"date":"14:44 07/04","title":"Ng\u00f4i sao Neymar c\u00f4ng khai h\u00f4n b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i trong r\u1ea1p h\u00e1t","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/7/ngoi-sao-neymar-cong-khai-hon-ban-gai-trong-rap-hat.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absol