d-position:-16px -224px}.ui-icon-grip-solid-vertical{background-position:-32px -224px}.ui-icon-grip-solid-horizontal{background-position:-48px -224px}.ui-icon-gripsmall-diagonal-se{background-position:-64px -224px}.ui-icon-grip-diagonal-se{background-position:-80px -224px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-tl{border-top-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-tr{border-top-right-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u00fd ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn b\u1ecb &lsquo;treo gi\u00f2&rsquo; t\u1edbi h\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c x\u1eed ph\u1ea1t qu\u00e1 n\u1eb7ng, b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf v\u1eabn c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 nh\u1eb9.<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa HAGL v\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby t\u1ed1i 5/4, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha b\u1ecf b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea1p ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ed7 Duy M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn b\u1ecb tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh tru\u1ea5t quy\u1ec1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u, gi\u00e1n ti\u1ebfp khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn thua \u0111\u1eadm tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i V-League 2018.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bau Duc muon dau tranh den cung.\" title=\"B\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea5u tranh \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/24/bau-duc-len-tieng-ve-quyet-dinh-treo-gio-tang-tien.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>B\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2 T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u1eb9</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c x\u1eed ph\u1ea1t n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 treo gi\u00f2 T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng tr\u00e1i chi\u1ec1u trong d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn. V\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u00ednh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n Vnexpress, \u00f4ng b\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u00f3 xem qua truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh, xem \u0111i xem l\u1ea1i t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tranh ch\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Duy M\u1ea1nh. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t pha v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o. Pha b\u00f3ng \u1ea5y qu\u00e1 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ph\u1ea1t th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf l\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang. L\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ai l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea1p th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf? T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t b\u1ee9c x\u00fac n\u00ean ra \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 nh\u1eb9 v\u00e0 v\u1eabn t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>&ldquo;L\u1ebd ra t\u00f4i c\u1ea5m lu\u00f4n c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a \u0111\u1ea5y, h\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 nh\u1eb9 v\u00e0 c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1eeda sai. T\u1eeb l\u00fac l\u00e0m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng s\u1ed1ng chung v\u1edbi b\u1ea1o l\u1ef1c. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do v\u00ec sao t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o ra h\u00e0ng tr\u0103m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi \u1edf h\u1ecd \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ee9c, h\u1ecdc v\u1ea5n r\u1ed3i m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. T\u00f4i \u0111ang ch\u1ed1ng ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, v\u1eady th\u00ec t\u1ea1i sao t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i dung d\u01b0\u1ee1ng cho ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c ch\u1ee9. Ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ecb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc, sau \u0111\u00f3 m\u1edbi l\u00e0m g\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c&rdquo;, v\u1ecb ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch HAGL tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ed1ng ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t. \u00d4ng t\u1eebng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd \u0111u\u1ed5i th\u1eb3ng c\u1ed5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o. Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, v\u1ecb ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch HAGL t\u1eebng &quot;c\u1ea5m c\u1eeda&quot; h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 V\u0103n Kh\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a SLNA t\u1ea1i U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00ec ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u. <o:p></o:p>Tuy v\u1eady, \u00f4ng c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf ra 400 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng cho Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y tr\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng cho c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n Anh Khoa c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&#10;Roboto;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;color:#081F2C;mso-fareast-language:KO\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thanh-luong-an-phat-cua-bau-duc-co-phan-vo-ly-168-183648.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/5/thanh-luong-an-phat-cua-bau-duc-co-phan-vo-ly.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thanh-luong-an-phat-cua-bau-duc-co-phan-vo-ly-168-183648.html\">Th\u00e0nh L\u01b0\u01a1ng: \u00c1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n v\u00f4 l\u00fd</span><br>\r\nN\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t treo gi\u00f2 h\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i V-League m\u00e0 T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i cho r\u1eb1ng \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u00e