 g\u00f3p g\u00ec cho Bayern Munich \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb g\u00e3y b\u00e0n ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i khi\u1ebfn anh ph\u1ea3i ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bayern Munich mua Stegen thay Manuel Neuer hinh anh\" title=\"Bayern Munich mua Stegen thay Manuel Neuer h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/25/Bayern-Munich-mua-Stegen-thay-Manuel-Neuer-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Neuer ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nSau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng, ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Sevilla \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn \u0111ang trong th\u1eddi gian h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft khi n\u00e0o anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Ngay c\u1ea3 khi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, Neuer v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Bayern l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bayern Munich d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111ang lo l\u1eafng v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 Neuer g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi. Bayern Munich mua <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/marcandre-ter-stegen-44449.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Stegen</strong></span> c\u1ee7a Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Don Balon \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Ter Stegen\" title=\"thu mon Ter Stegen\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/23/bayern-munich-tinh-gay-soc-voi-thu-mon-cua-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bayern Munich mua Stegen \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Manuel Neuer \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 32 bu\u1ed9c Bayern ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u1ebb h\u01a1n, v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn Stegen c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/barcelona-37.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Barca</strong></span>. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou, anh c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, song Bayern Munich d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Theo Don Balon,&nbsp;&ldquo;H\u00f9m x\u00e1m&rdquo; ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 chi ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady nh\u01b0ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Bayern Munich mua Stegen th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1eabn l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao. Barca \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Camp Nou, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng cam k\u1ebft g\u1eafn b\u00f3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi Barca.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Bayern Munich th\u00ec <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/khung-khiep-mu-chi-89-trieu-bang-mua-thu-mon-cua-barca-172-181223.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>MU c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Stegen</strong></span>, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf nh\u1eafm th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Barca trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p David de Gea c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real Madrid.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Stegen \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/88625-42556/033100\" target=\"_blank\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Stegen \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"856","checkdouble":"183713"},{"date":"21:52 06/04","title":"Carles Puyol ch\u1ecdn ra trung v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/6/carles-puyol-chon-ra-hau-ve-xuat-sac-nhat-the-gioi.PNG","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}.articlerelate2{padding